headline: Cornelis CN5000 Deployed by U.S. Department of Energy’s National Nuclear Security Administration at Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory
summary: WAYNE, Pa., July 23, 2025--Cornelis Networks, a leading provider of intelligent, high-performance networking solutions, today announced that the CN5000 is being deployed by the U.S. Department of Energy’s (DOE) National Nuclear Security Administration (NNSA) to power the 952-node "Lynx" cluster at Lawrence Livermore National Laboratory (LLNL).
